title: 645 of the best Rock Songs Ever
description:
645 of the best Rock Songs Ever:

Are these the greatest 645 Rock songs ever?
I would say yes. ...But "best ever" and "greatest" type terms are subjective to your tastes. Note I used "of the" in the title. I won&#039;t presume to think this is everything. There is bound to be a few of somebody&#039;s personal favorites omitted (especially newer stuff). You should, however, find a ton of good stuff in here and not much you will hate, unless you suck of course! ;-)

Why did I share this?
I&#039;m sick of seeing these so-called "Greatest ### Songs of all time" torrents that really seemed to be filled with schlock. Again, it&#039;s subjective, but when you&#039;ve got 500 songs, it&#039;s hard to justify leaving certain all time classics out.

What is it?
This is stuff from my personal collection. I normalized the volume of this pack (to 93 Db) so you won&#039;t have dead quiet levels on one song and then ear shattering loudness on the next track. All are .mp3 format. Most (95%) are high bit rates, 192 to 320, with a few scattered 160 and the very rare (like 5 or so) 128 bitrate songs. I separated them into 3 categories of: Rock, Lite Rock and Hard Rock. This may not be perfect either, so sue me?

Why 645 songs? Why not 500? ...or 734?
This torrent, at 4.37GB, just barely fits on one DVD. I suppose I could have re-encoded everything to 192, but hey, I&#039;m lazy. You&#039;re lucky I bothered to segregate these songs from my collection and share them! So? 645 it is!

Seeding/connection:
I will share this until seeded, but after that, you folks are essentially on your own. My connection isn&#039;t the greatest (~50 or so kbps upload), so this will take a few days to seed. (afterwards, I want my upload speed back for ME damnit!) If my seed disappears, have no fear, I will have it back up shortly. If I check back weeks/months later and there&#039;s someone dying for a re-seed, I may have a heart and do it, but no guarantees. I am after all, a heartless prick.

Feel free to share this elsewhere, it&#039;s not like I have any rights to this. :-D
